flowchart LR
  DEV[Developer or reviewer] --> REPO[GitHub repository]
  REPO --> CHECKS[Lint, typecheck, tests, build]
  REPO --> HOST[Next.js hosting target]

  HOST --> SUPABASE[Supabase Auth, Postgres, Storage]
  HOST --> STRIPE[Stripe Checkout, Portal, Webhooks]
  HOST --> AI[AI provider abstraction]
  HOST --> LOGS[Runtime logs and audit trails]

  SUPABASE --> APPDATA[Operational, billing, analytics, AI run data]
  STRIPE --> WEBHOOK[Webhook route]
  WEBHOOK --> APPDATA
